&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of experience in construction coordination, field engineering, or similar role (internship experience considered).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in industrial, high-tech, or semiconductor construction environments is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of construction processes, sequencing, and field coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read and interpret construction drawings (P&amp;amp;IDs, layouts, electrical/mechanical plans).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and multitasking skills in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective communication skills with both technical teams and field personnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem-solving mindset with the ability to identify and escalate issues proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of construction processes, sequencing, and field coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
